title: Middle.Earth.Shadow.of.Mordor.HD.Texture.Pack.Addon-CODEX
description:
CODEX PRESENTS:
  
           Middle-Earth: Shadow of Mordor - HD Texture Pack Addon 

    Release Date :  9/2014                         Protection : Steam
    Discs        :  1                              Genre      : Action 

     
 
   This pack will add to the game quality high definition textures.
    

     
   
   - Extract
   - Run setup.exe and install texture pack to your gamedir
   - Copy crack from CODEX folder to your installdir
   - Play
   
   Notes: This patch requires: CODEX release of ME: Shadow of Mordor
   
     
   Block game exe in your firewall to prevent the game from trying to go
   online ..
